1993;;The Real McCoy;;American;;Russell Mulcahy;;Kim Basinger, Val Kilmer, Terence Stamp;;crime drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Real_McCoy_(film);;Karen McCoy (Kim Basinger) is released from prison with nothing but the clothes on her back. Before being incarcerated, Karen was the bank robber of her time, but now she wishes for nothing more than to settle down and start a new life.Unfortunately, between a dirty parole officer, old business partners, and an idiot ex-husband, McCoy will have to do the unthinkable to save her son (Zack English) and new heartthrob J.T. (Val Kilmer): Another bank job.